wikipedia_page.main: Matthew James Lamb  (born 19 July 1996) is an English cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Warwickshire on 6 September 2016 in the 2016 County Championship. He made his List A debut for Warwickshire in the 2017 Royal London One-Day Cup on 5 May 2017. He made his Twenty20 debut on 11 August 2019, for Warwickshire in the 2019 t20 Blast.
